title: Mapping Abortion Access Across the U.S (Guttmacher Institute, U.S)
description: This project explores key data points related to abortion in the U.S, using data from Guttmacher Institute's documentation on abortion numbers, rates, and related indicators. It includes visualizations and analysis to further understand the variation of healthcare and abortion access across regions.
